answer.full_answer: Yes, the app declares the collection of data.

reply.reference: We obtain information about you when you use our website, such as when you contact us about products and services, or when you sign up to and participate in a programme provided by us to your employer organisation. The personal information we might collect from you includes your name, email address and work postal address. It may also include information regarding what website pages are accessed and when. URL: https://gogreenrewards.teamjump.co.uk/privacy-policy

reply.question: 3. Does the app declare the purpose of data collection and use?

answer.full_answer: Yes, the app declares the purpose of data collection and use to administer the scheme, display user information in the program leaderboard, seek feedback on services, handle competition entries, send sustainability updates, and notify users of service changes.

reply.analysis: The privacy policy clearly states the specific purposes for which user data is collected and used.
reply.reference: We may use your information to: - Administer the scheme, including sending weekly reminder emails...- Show your first name, initial of surname and Green Points total...- Seek your views or comments on the services we provide...- Deal with entries into a competition...- Send you quarterly updates about sustainability news and innovation...- Notify you of changes to our services...URL: https://gogreenrewards.teamjump.co.uk/privacy-policy

reply.question: 5. Does the app share data with third parties?

answer.full_answer: Yes, the app shares data with third parties when necessary for processing voucher requests and program administration.

reply.analysis: The privacy policy clearly states that data, including name and email address, may be shared with specific third parties for purposes related to voucher requests and program administration.
reply.reference: In order to process voucher requests we may share your order details, including name and postal address, with our suppliers so that your order can be fulfilled. As part of the administration of the programme your details, including name and email address, may be passed onto the sustainability team at the North London NHS Mental Health Partnership so that they can contact you directly with regards to Go Green Rewards. Your details will not be shared with any other parties nor be used to contact you for any other reason. URL: https://gogreenrewards.teamjump.co.uk/privacy-policy
